56
00:03:43.790 --> 00:03:46.150
Make groups of 4 bits from right to left 

57
00:03:46.450 --> 00:03:49.850
and replace each group with corresponding hexadecimal value 

58
00:03:50.410 --> 00:03:55.420
So we have a binary value here : 10001101

59
